ink?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180823%2Fs00001%2F1535005753191&d=WAyJM2esBSIt0x96w2cgdy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=af240157\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180823%2Fs00001%2F1535005753191&h=e6342b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180823/s00001/1535005753191</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:43:51.000Z","msg":"大陸美好生活？<br />\n狗也不屌 平既去台灣泰國越南都唔係中国囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba01b512df2b25205ad432f73cb452117d5d1b6c","tid":790590,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"北方大媽幾時返北方故鄉"},{"pid":"cf2d39250d90b0703c3e8d8248ea5e6805be7cea","tid":790590,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:45:11.000Z","msg":"好彩十幾萬果陣買左層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4ae435715dc2a17e5514aceeecaeac551d405f","tid":790590,"uid":18728,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"咁所有新移民即刻轉送佢地去「更美好生活」嘅地方先"},{"pid":"e3607f5733035bcaf0b139be77aa471cee35b656","tid":790590,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:46:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0d37576dac89a24f58b959423db11b335874b2c","tid":790590,"uid":45353,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"西藏咪又係類似概念<br />\n<br />\n比著數班中產北佬係西藏發展<br />\n反之窮西藏人出其他省工作人工高做利誘出走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果而家西藏比北佬霸哂<br />\n出去做野果班本地人變無業遊民<br />\n就算留底係度都比北佬騎住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇西藏被侵略個過程<br />\n唔會完全一樣<br />\n但熟口熟面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf18736b59b4e6956a3973697fb1cb25f4fd49f6","tid":790590,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"